order_number.orig_str: शासन निर्णय क्रमांकः उपकें-२०२४/ प्र.क्र.२३४/ आरोग्य-४

para_trans: Mauje Ghatnandur, Ta. Regarding sanction of new Health Sub-centre at Bhum, G. Dharashiv as a special case.
Government Decision No: Sub-Collector-2024 / P.No.234 / Health-4

Read: - Letter from Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries) Mumbai No: ASH / Rooms-7A / T-8 / Ghatnandur / Sub-Centre / Establishment / Dharashiv / 2239-41/24, dated 06.06.2024.
Introduction: - Mauje Ghatnandur, Ta. Health facilities to the citizens of the area at Bhum, Dist. Dharashiv
A new health sub-centre needs to be sanctioned in line with the supply, so a health sub-centre is to be set up at the site.
Approval was under consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Mauje Ghatnandur, Ta. New Health Sub-Centre approved as "Special Case" at Bhum, Dist. Dharashiv
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
